    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "巢父"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（巢父牵牛上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "心比寒梅澈骨清，"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "孤芳自赏乐天真。"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "扑去污人三斗尘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老汉，巢父。自幼秉性清高，为人固执，生在如今世界，语言动静俱不合时宜；"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "因此隐居山林，与世人不通往来，自种自食，日出而作，日入而息，任天行"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乐，却也逍遥自在。村中有一人许由，也是个清洁君子，我与他为友，颇甚相"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得。看溪边水清，不免牵牛去饮便了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "牵牛去向溪边饮，"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 4,
          "唱": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 1.0,
        "dominant_style_family": "西皮",
        "musical_styles": [
          "西皮原板",
          "西皮摇板"
        ]
      },
      "scene_feature": [
