    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "巢父",
        "许由"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（许由上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "许由",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "匆匆掩耳向前走，"
        },
        {
          "character": "许由",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "口出污言不自羞。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（许由洗耳。巢父牵牛上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你因何洗耳说原由。"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "许先生请了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "许由",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是巢老先生！"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何故在此洗耳？"
        },
        {
          "character": "许由",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再休提起。今日我正在家中，忽听户外人声马嘶，叩门相访。想你我向不与人"
        },
        {
          "character": "许由",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相交，况高车驷马，富贵之人，忽然造访，岂不是一件大大的怪事！"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "真是件怪事。但不知是何人来访？"
        },
        {
          "character": "许由",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是我隔门偷觑偷觑，你道是谁？原来是皇帝亲到我家来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我却不知你几时与皇帝结交？以后我就不敢高攀了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "许由",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我哪里与他结交？是他自来寻我，我和他素不相识！况且分隔云泥，还是不见"
        },
        {
          "character": "许由",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为妙，因此我从后门逃走。"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好朋友！真与我同心。他乃专制之君，我们是自由之民，薰莸不同器，公私不"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两立，哪里能说到一处？不见的为妙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "许由",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎奈他赶到荒郊，与我相见，他言道：家天下不如官天下，天下乃人人之天下，"
        },
        {
          "character": "许由",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非一人之天下，所以不传于子而传于贤。苦苦将天下让与我许由，这等污耳"
        },
        {
          "character": "许由",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "之言，我哪里能听？因此掩耳到此，用溪中清水，洗我耳中污言，老先生你想"
        },
        {
          "character": "许由",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这件事，岂不是一件大大的怪事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "闻言不觉怒心头，"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "顿足捶胸恨许由。"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "全不管这浊水污我的牛！"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "可惜这清流变浊流。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（巢父气愤，牵牛走去，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "许由",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "可笑巢父没来由，"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
